ActGeneral Campaign Star and General Service Medal Regulations, 2009
SubjectOrder Awarding of the General Campaign Star with the EXPEDITION ribbon
PrecisOrder determining who has rendered service that is worthy of recognition by the award of to the General Campaign Star with the EXPEDITION ribbon(service in the presence of an armed enemy); and establishing its order of precedence in the Canadian Honours System.
